{"tid":1931203,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"《南華早報》員工透露：辦公室逾半同事冇戴口罩","createTime":"2020-03-18T04:59:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T06:30:06.000Z","uid":5195,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"abf4be38e0b274e9e6476a716d2f4c203af62d11","tid":1931203,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T04:59:17.000Z","msg":"《南華早報》電郵指出，該員工曾於本月10至13日、16日在時代廣場辦公室上班，亦曾使用員工休息室及酒吧；銅鑼灣時代廣場及黃竹坑辦公室本周關閉，已通知時代廣場管業處並安排徹底清潔辦公室，員工在家工作。<br />\n<br />\n有《南華早報》員工透露，公司在疫情下仍開放員工酒吧，逢周五如常提供免費暢飲，惟農曆年後公司已安排員工在家工作一個月，估計未有太多員工使用。另有員工稱，辦公室內逾半同事沒戴口罩，包括外籍及本地同事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200318/s00001/1584489641539/《南華早報》有員工初步確診新冠肺炎-曾用休息室及酒吧\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200318%2Fs00001%2F1584489641539%2F%E3%80%8A%E5%8D%97%E8%8F%AF%E6%97%A9%E5%A0%B1%E3%80%8B%E6%9C%89%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%9B%BE%E7%94%A8%E4%BC%91%E6%81%AF%E5%AE%A4%E5%8F%8A%E9%85%92%E5%90%A7&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqFxzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=cbd414b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200318%2Fs00001%2F1584489641539%2F%E3%80%8A%E5%8D%97%E8%8F%AF%E6%97%A9%E5%A0%B1%E3%80%8B%E6%9C%89%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%9B%BE%E7%94%A8%E4%BC%91%E6%81%AF%E5%AE%A4%E5%8F%8A%E9%85%92%E5%90%A7&h=a21c5bc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200318/s00001/1584489641539/《南華早報》有員工初步確診新冠肺炎-曾用休息室及酒吧</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6b87872854ca230021daa830db8e3e1b247ce05","tid":1931203,"uid":107681,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18